# 🌐 Anjali.dev – Portfolio Website

This is my first personal portfolio website built using HTML and CSS.

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 https://anjalisharma450865-alt.github.io/Portfolio-Website/

## ✨ Features

* Responsive design
* Smooth scrolling navigation
* Modern UI with animations
* Sections: Home, About, Projects, Contact

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML
* CSS

## 📂 Sections Included

* **Home** – Introduction and headline
* **About** – Brief about me
* **Projects** – My work showcase
* **Contact** – How to reach me

